title: Are You Seeing The World Incorrectly?

description:
Episode 632 - Perception is reality. However you see the world, is how you what you will carry with you the rest of the day. So how do we change our perception, if it is indeed what creates our reality? I'm going to talk about that in this episode! Follow me on Instagram: https://instagram.com/robdialjr
